<h3>Parking</h3>
<p>There are large car parks for patients and visitors, for which charges apply. To view charges, please vlew our website. Some visitors are exempt from payment: eg: parents staying overnight with very sick children; patients undergoing treatment such as radiotherapy; parents feeding babies on the Neo Natal Unit. <br/>&lt;a href=”http://www.gloshospitals.org.uk/content/transport.html”&gt;click here&lt;/a&gt;</p>
